<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AuraStyle AI | The Future of Personal Fit</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@200;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --cream: #F2F1EC;
            --charcoal: #1A1A1A;
            --gold: #A6915B;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--charcoal);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .logo-main {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content-grid {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: -50px auto 100px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        h2 {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        p { line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }

        .highlight { font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) { .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="Aurastyle1.png" alt="AuraStyle AI" class="logo-main">
    </header>

    <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>The Strategic Vision</h2>
            <p>AuraStyle AI is a <span class="highlight">B2B SaaS integration</span> designed to partner with major apparel retailers. By utilizing <span class="highlight">Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs)</span> for precise body shape analysis, we bridge the gap between digital shopping and personal fit.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Business Impact</h2>
            <p>Our data-driven approach is projected to <span class="highlight">reduce return rates by 25%</span>, providing a clear ROI for retailers while fostering a more <span class="highlight">sustainable fashion ecosystem</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 2;">
            <h2>Ethical AI Framework</h2>
            <p>We prioritize user safety. All biometric data is processed via <span class="highlight">Edge Computing</span>, ensuring photos never leave the user's device. Our models are audited for <span class="highlight">Fit Fairness</span> to ensure inclusivity.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        Juana Mathurin | Westchester College | 2026
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
